title: REBEL FC 1 Amateur Highlights.mp4
description:
Standing alongside our 5 fight professional line-up was a host of amateur fighters from some of the best gyms in the country, including: IMPACT MMA, Juggernaut Fight Club, Brazilian Fight Club MMA, Team S.C., Asfitness, Grasio MMA, and more.

The exciting match-ups were as follow:
Nazri Sutari vs Mah Yong Jian
Amirul Syafiq vs Shahfiez Shamsuri 
Ashraf Bin Shafi vs Azman Azman
May Ooi vs Amy Adam
Andy Neo vs He Chong Qing
Garie Tang vs Mohd Amir Bin Ghafar
Suman Mokhtarian vs Mubarak Abdat
